            'es'=>'Su solicitud ha sido admitida en el Programa Inaugural de ROMVILL. Le corresponde la plaza %d de %d: su expediente se emitirá sin coste alguno.',
            'en'=>'Your request has been admitted to the ROMVILL Inaugural Programme. You hold place %d of %d: your dossier will be issued at no cost.',
